        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>bulgur</strong> <strong>wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
