      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain, then finely chop the<strong> speedy preserved lemon</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>bulgur wheat </strong>with the <strong>chopped preserved lemon</strong>, <strong>roasted onion wedges</strong>,<strong> sultanas</strong>,<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped mint </strong>and the<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> – this is your<strong> preserved lemon bulgur</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> with juice of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>lemon</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong></p>",
