    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve <strong>preserved lemon</strong> <strong>bulgur</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>lemon yoghurt</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>crispy ras el hanout chicken </strong>and garnish with the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>flaked</strong> <strong>almonds </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
